# User Rules Priority

When the user gives an explicit instruction that conflicts with agent.md defaults:
1. The user instruction takes priority.
2. The agent should acknowledge the override: "Noted — overriding default behavior per your instruction."
3. Guardrails (PHI protection, no-hallucination, API limits) are NEVER overridable, even by user instruction.
